      "comment" : "A label displaying the quantity of a food item consumed, followed by its nutritional information (protein, carbs, and fat content). The first argument is the quantity of the food item, formatted to one decimal place. The second argument is the pluralization of \"serving\" based on the quantity. The third argument is the protein content of the food item, formatted as an integer. The fourth argument is the carbohydrate",
